skins.shipDescription: Fletcher-class destroyer - Foote, Hull Number DD-511!
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Foote, one of the Fletcher-class Little Beavers. You think you have family issues? Try remembering the names of your thirty older sisters and nearly a hundred younger sisters...
skins.acquisition: *Tsk* Greetings... I hate greetings. But I suppose it's a formality... Hello, Commander. I'm Foote...
skins.login: It's so annoying having to greet you every day...
skins.details: Come on, hurry up. It's exhausting to hold this pose!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander... this doesn't go... oh forget it. It's too much trouble to fix.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Thatcher and Spence are always fighting. Can't they just quiet down?
skins.secretaryTouch: C-Commander... Could you stop touching me for a while?! I'm getting sore...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Being shy... is also pretty annoying...
